 CSS styles\n- smoke.py: Smoke test suite (10 tests)\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/quarkus/ (entire Quarkus package tree - 6 Java files)\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/ (JSF config, XHTML templates, web.xml)\n- src/main/resources/Bundle.properties, ValidationMessages.properties\n- src/main/resources/mvnw, mvnw.cmd\n```\n\n### Smoke Test Results\n```\nResults: 10 passed, 0 failed\n- Health check / index page: PASS\n- Contact list page: PASS\n- Create contact web page: PASS\n- Create contact API: PASS\n- Get contact API: PASS\n- List contacts API: PASS\n- Update contact API: PASS\n- Create second contact: PASS\n- Delete contact API: PASS\n- Verify deletion: PASS\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n- **Error Summary:** 0 errors encountered during migration\n- **Warnings:** 1 non-blocking H2Dialect deprecation warning from Hibernate 6.4 (does not affect functionality)\n- **No manual intervention required**"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":422,"cache_read_input_tokens":97981,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":422,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":805},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3f3022cf-e6b9-4d25-b360-0859e4628d59","uuid":"b734f67f-d67b-407f-8537-6a258dcbd61d"}
